node.text:
To my son ,
Thank you for changing my life. I finally developed a love that is so unconditional. I promise to protect you & I promise to give you the world because you deserve it 💙 love you forever ! 05/03/21 👶🏽

node.text: I’ve been waiting my 9 months to meet you little one. This journey hasn’t been easy, especially what’s still ahead of us, but knowing we get to meet you at the other end of it makes it all worth it 👶🏽✨ 05/08 (stay tuned for these pictures 🤞🏽)
